      • CompletionRequest

        public CompletionRequest(TransactionReferences transactionReferences)
        Creates a new CompletionRequest with the TransactionReferences of the transaction to complete.

        Note that the given transaction reference values are copied.

        Parameters:
        transactionReferences - the transaction references of the transaction to reverse. This parameter must not be null.
